{
  "text": "HUVEC cells were cultured in 6-well plates at 0,5 \u00d7 10 6 cells per well. After a 48-hour period for reaching confl uence, cells were exposed for 4 hours to iron/ascorbate with or without the antioxidant substrates and then were incubated for 2 h at 37 \u00b0C in 0.5 ml of supplemented EBM with 5% v/v LPDS containing [ 3 H]-cholesteryl hexadecyl ether-oxLDL (12,5 \u00b5g/ml). To determine the non-specifi c binding, cells were incubated with labeled-oxLDL in the presence of a 50-fold excess of unlabeled oxLDL. The assays were essentially carried out as previously described [CITATION_1] [CITATION_2] ).",
